com.variant.client.servlet

Interface ServletSession

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.variant.client.Session
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ServletSessionImpl

    public interface ServletSession
extends com.variant.client.Session

    Servlet-aware wrapper around bare client's implementation of Session. Overrides the Session.targetForState(State) method to return the narrower, Servlet-aware state request object ServletStateRequest.

    Since:
    1.0
